name: On The Road, drawing, Chicago, IL 2017-2021
description: 1 of 1 original artwork sent to the collector, includes international shipping. On The Road, drawing on rocks with non-toxic paint in Chicago, IL. Photo 2017, drawing 2021, a collaboration between Theo Coulombe x Shantell Martin. Size: 24 x 35 3/4 inches, 61 x 90.8 cms. Medium: Ink on pigment print from Tri-X 400, 35mm negative film. At the end of the road...freedom. To BE.
